SudokuGUI

Class SudokuCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • SudokuGUI.SudokuCell

  • public class SudokuCell
extends java.lang.Object
    This class draws out each of the specific cells in the Sudoku game board. These can later be replicated into a 9 by 9 square to form the whole Sudoku board. The first few methods are direct methods that return specific values that could be accessed by other people. The draw method is basically the main focus of this class; it shows how the cell is created and how it is drawn.
    Author:
    Eric Cheng, Kabir Kapoor, Assignment - JMCh00_SudokuFinal
